Euronext Reports ‘Technical Issues’ With Receiving Order Acknowledgements

-- B y   A l e x i s   X y d i a s
-- 
2011-09-14T06:40:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-14/euronext-reports-technical-issues-with-receiving-order-acknowledgements.html
NYSE Euronext (NYX)  said it’s
“experiencing technical issues with the order acknowledgement”
in its equities and bonds market. The operator of the Paris and
Amsterdam exchanges commented on its website at 8:33 a.m. in
Paris.  The incident is under investigation, the company said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alexis Xydias at 
 axydias@bloomberg.net  